productiontracker

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • productiontracker.Product
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioPlayer, MoviePlayer

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
    Primary Object used in this program. Product represents items that can be produced in the production line tracker. Once product exists in the program, it can be used to create production records.
